 detailed, Leif revealed |url=https://www.polygon.com/2020/3/26/21195302/animal-crossing-new-horizons-bunny-day-event-leif |website=Polygon |accessdate=19 April 2020 |date=26 March 2020}}</ref>\n\n}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{official website|http://www.animal-crossing.com/}}\n\n{{Animal Crossing series}}\n\n[[Category:Animal Crossing]]\n[[Category:Lists of video game characters|Animal Crossing]]\n[[Category:Lists of Nintendo characters]]\n", "name_user": "Morgan695", "label": "safe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Characters_in_the_Animal_Crossing_series"}
